Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.86,0:02:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然!不请自来的小娇妻!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.24,0:02:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帐~~~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.91,0:02:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帐~~~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帐~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.55,0:02:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少挡老子的路~~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.33,0:02:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨~大家早啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.83,0:02:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也要打起精神上课喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?老师，那个戒指是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.41,0:03:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，被发现了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.34,0:03:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,婚礼是什么时候啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.54,0:03:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菜搞老师，难道你要结婚了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公是怎样的人啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.35,0:03:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌啦，真是~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.62,0:03:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么啦岩城同学\N老师要结婚了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.02,0:03:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，那又怎样\N跟我又没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.23,0:03:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么婚礼嘛!什么结婚嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.84,0:03:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帐~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.29,0:03:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去，真是超不爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.89,0:03:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之啊我没学到教训
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.26,0:03:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又为了比我年长的女人失恋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.23,0:04:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去!我怎么老是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.60,0:04:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回来啦!老公~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于见到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.11,0:04:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一天我已经等了好久好久了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.78,0:04:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公?老公你在哪儿啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.09,0:04:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快，快挂了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.29,0:04:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌啦，怎么在那种地方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你你你、你谁啊你!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.53,0:04:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!这样不行这样不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.24,0:04:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉没有事先说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.74,0:04:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我从今天起正式成为您的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫莉采儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.54,0:04:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是妻子耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...不会是脑袋秀逗了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.18,0:04:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连入籍都办好了，你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这、这啥啊!?我才15岁耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这叫国家权力!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.06,0:05:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什什、什么啊?你们这群欧吉桑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待在那种地方做什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.27,0:05:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不是欧吉桑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.14,0:05:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干爹!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干、干爹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是干爹!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你们那么说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老爸!老妈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是年轻貌美的干妈们就好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问题不在那儿吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.35,0:05:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别那么兴奋嘛，老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.15,0:05:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天可是我们的结婚纪念日啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.67,0:05:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿可是以某DNA为基础
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.50,0:05:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结合了国家最先进的技术所\N造出之细胞集合体的原型人种啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少跟我说那些莫名其妙的东西!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.62,0:05:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊哈，第一次惹老公生气\N又第一次被扔又第一次被摔耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.45,0:06:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不放开~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次被甩来甩去耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么就由我向各位说明吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.35,0:06:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为是国家机密所以一切无可奉告!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.42,0:06:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那算啥啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.49,0:06:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何，莉采儿成为你的妻子\N那已经是国家的决定事项了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不能让她哭泣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.23,0:06:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不可以喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要擅自作主!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，凭我丈夫那\N微薄的薪水光养这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.30,0:06:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正值发育期的孩子\N就已经够辛苦的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.44,0:06:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，对啊\N我连自己的书房都没有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且这间房子还有\N30多年的利息要缴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.18,0:07:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这之上要是\N家里人再增加的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.95,0:07:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的零用钱可是零\N零耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你直升部长...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.32,0:07:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终生免缴水电费和\N医疗建保费...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房屋贷款从此\N一笔勾消...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚餐吃炒三鲜\N可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，太太，不用那么客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,球赛要开始了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么才一下\N大家就一团和气啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管老爸老妈是怎么想的\N反正我是不会承认的啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.48,0:07:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新婚初夜新郎应该要把新娘子\N抱到床上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.85,0:07:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新娘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀，老公你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌啦，性子那么急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.07,0:07:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只对年长的女人\N有兴趣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 这辈子都不会\N把你放在眼里的啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.08,0:08:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.94,0:08:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要比你年长就可以了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，只要你能的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我会加油的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白~痴!那种事是不可能的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.82,0:08:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我年幼就是一辈子比我年幼\N比我年长就是一辈子比我年长啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且不管怎么看你都只是小学生嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本没什么好说的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.53,0:08:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何都不行吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.47,0:08:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎样都...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少烦我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.24,0:08:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可能会哭喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.34,0:08:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种把戏对我没用啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.71,0:08:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能让她哭啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿，不可以哭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是好孩子要忍耐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.45,0:08:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍一忍，忍一忍嘛\N莉采儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.35,0:08:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别哭\N别哭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.72,0:08:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点到避难所去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.63,0:08:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么避难所啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.96,0:08:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.01,0:09:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么\N没什么好说的呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.38,0:09:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公你这个大笨蛋~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.25,0:09:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不快收回你刚刚说的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个家会完蛋的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.18,0:09:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这这、这是什么啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.38,0:09:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿眼泪的成分\N几乎跟硝化甘油一样啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变成这样我们也阻止不了了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别哭啦，莉采儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就先让你住下来啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.51,0:09:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.51,0:09:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千真万确吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还能怎么办啊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.78,0:09:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公我最喜欢你了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.18,0:09:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没说你可以抱我~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.79,0:09:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次被老公丢向夕阳耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种程度很快就能修复了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.56,0:10:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算全部被炸毁也只要两三天就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.73,0:10:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种时候，机密费用还真是好用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.07,0:10:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁炒三鲜冷掉之前\N快来吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.70,0:10:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来来，啤酒再多喝点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.32,0:10:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯~好让人期待喔\N新婚初夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌啦!\N是初夜耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.09,0:10:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公再等一下唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.83,0:10:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好倒楣的一天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛!\N至少先敲个门吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.37,0:11:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小女子不才，还请您多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛打扮成这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.47,0:11:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌啦!新婚初夜\N当然要穿长襦绊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.81,0:11:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.48,0:11:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先进来罗~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂喂喂喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.32,0:11:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌，老公你怎么那么猴急嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在打什么鬼主意啊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.62,0:11:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,图书馆的书上有写说新婚夫妻要在\N同一个被窝里做“好事”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.49,0:11:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那什么书啊!要睡到别的房间去睡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不不不，不要哭啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我能在这房间睡吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去!真拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.40,0:11:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我睡罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.51,0:11:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是那里!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.54,0:11:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的位置在这儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.18,0:12:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.55,0:12:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你对我这么温柔\N我好高兴喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.02,0:12:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说什么傻话\N哪里算温柔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.82,0:12:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然讲的那么不情愿的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是还是让我睡同一间房间了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.83,0:12:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因为让你哭的话就麻烦大啦\N白痴~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.81,0:12:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，等一等\N不行、别哭、别哭啊!
