Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.38,0:13:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人和女人真是难以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.75,0:13:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了查清楚我去了图书馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.42,0:13:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然对比他年幼的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公是一点兴趣也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.73,0:13:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是人家好喜欢你\N所以我不会哭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.51,0:13:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不气馁，不逃避\N更不会失去勇气
